---
// About section component
---

<section id="about" class="min-h-screen flex items-center py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="text-emerald-400">About</span> Me
      </h2>
      <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
      <!-- Text content -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm an honest, competitive, and fast-learning individual with a strong passion for 
          <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Computer Vision</span>, 
          <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">AI Agents</span>, and 
          <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Data Engineering</span>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm experienced in building and orchestrating AI agents and data workflows, including 
          task automation, model integration, and pipeline design. This includes hands-on experience 
          with workflow orchestration tools like <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">Apache Airflow</span> 
          and cloud services with <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">AWS</span>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I completed my bachelor's degree with a thesis focused on 
          <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Indonesian Lip Reading</span>—a deep learning-based 
          approach to modeling complex visual patterns. Through this project, I gained proficiency with 
          major frameworks like <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">PyTorch</span> and 
          <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">TensorFlow</span>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm fluent in <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">Python</span>, <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">SQL</span>, 
          and <span class="font-mono text-emerald-300">R</span>, with hands-on experience across the data and 
          ML stack. As an AWS Academy Graduate in Data Engineering, I'm certified and ready to tackle 
          scalable data challenges.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I value <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">GREATNESS in teamwork</span> and approach 
          every challenge by identifying root causes and delivering effective, scalable solutions. 
          My philosophy: solve it right the first time, and make it count.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Skills cards -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-emerald-400 font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></span>
            Core Skills
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm">
            <li>• Computer Vision</li>
            <li>• LLM & AI Agents</li>
            <li>• Data Engineering</li>
            <li>• ML Deployments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-emerald-400 font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></span>
            Technologies
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm font-mono">
            <li>• Python, SQL, R</li>
            <li>• PyTorch, TensorFlow</li>
            <li>• AWS, Docker</li>
            <li>• Apache Airflow</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-emerald-400 font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></span>
            Certification
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">AWS Academy Graduate<br />Data Engineering</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Floating accent elements -->
    <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-40 h-40 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-40 h-40 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      transparent 0%,
      rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.02) 50%,
      transparent 100%
    );
  }
</style>
